name: CryptoZoo
public_notice: CryptoZoo (ZOO) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this Twitter post.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
An autonomous ecosystem where ZOO owners breed, collect and trade exotic hybrid animals via NFTs!

The team consists of experts from across the field including Logan Paul, an NFT and Pokemon obsessive.
